oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Labor Day Celebration with Cal Smith at the Lions Club Park (17998)
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Smith, Cal; Young, Faron; Jim and Jesse; Cooper, Stoney, 1918-1977; Cooper, Wilma Lee, 1921-2011; Metal photoplates;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color half sheet (red and black on white) announcing the Labor Day Celebration with Cal Smith, Faron Young, Ken Allen, Jim and Jesse and others at the Lions Club Park on September 6. Poster features metal photoplates of Cal Smith, Faron Young, Ken Allen, Jim and Jesse, and Wilma Lee and Stoney Cooper. Poster was ordered by Ken Calendar (purchase order 17998). To view the paperwork associated with this poster, see https://digi.countrymusichalloffame.org/digital/collection/hatch3/id/20944.
